OL,3,CDetectives investigating arson attack
OL,4,Con mosque make three more arrests
OL,6,FThree more arrests have been made as
OL,7,Fpart of an investigation into an arson
OL,8,Fattack on a mosque in Peacehaven in
OL,9,FEast Sussex.
OL,11,FTwo people escaped uninjured from
OL,12,Finside the building on Phyllis Avenue
OL,13,Fon 4 October last year, when it was
OL,14,Freported a fire was started outside
OL,15,Fthe place of worship.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
