CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774455106
OL,3,CDetectives investigating arson attack
OL,4,Con mosque make three more arrests
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, counter-terror police
OL,7,Farrested a 36-year-old man from
OL,8,FEastbourne on suspicion of conspiracy
OL,9,Fto commit arson and a 38-year-old man
OL,10,Ffrom Brighton on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmalicious communication and criminal
OL,12,Fdamage.
OL,14,FA third man, a 42-year-old from
OL,15,FSaltdean was arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fmalicious communications and
OL,17,Fencouraging or assisting a crime.
OL,19,FThe trio have been released on bail
OL,20,Funtil 23 June.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
