PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774455106
OL,3,CDetectives investigating arson attack
OL,4,Con mosque make three more arrests
OL,6,FSussex Police superintendent Rachel
OL,7,FSwinney said: "We are continuing to
OL,8,Fwork closely with our colleagues in
OL,9,FCounter Terrorism Policing South East
OL,10,Fas they use specialist resources to
OL,11,Finvestigate the arson at the mosque in
OL,12,FPeacehaven.
OL,14,F"The incident caused understandable
OL,15,Fconcern within the local community
OL,16,Fsince it took place in October.
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
