PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774455106
OL,3,CDetectives investigating arson attack
OL,4,Con mosque make three more arrests
OL,6,F"These recent arrests form part of a
OL,7,Fpre-planned operation and there is no
OL,8,Fthreat to those in the community
OL,9,Fhowever people may notice search
OL,10,Factivity taking place at residential
OL,11,Fproperties while enquiries continue."
OL,13,FA fundraiser on GoFundMe to help
OL,14,Frepair the mosque and replace what was
OL,15,Fdamaged has raised more than #55,000.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@eO]
