CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774455106
OL,3,CDetectives investigating arson attack
OL,4,Con mosque make three more arrests
OL,6,FIt comes as two men, Ricky Ryder, 38,
OL,7,Fand Jack Slowey, 34, have already
OL,8,Fappeared in court in November last
OL,9,Fyear over the incident, charged with
OL,10,Farson with intent to endanger life and
OL,11,Ftwo further charges of arson relating
OL,12,Fto the vehicles.
OL,14,FThey are next due to appear at the Old
OL,15,FBailey in London for a plea hearing on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FMeanwhile a 70-year-old man from
OL,19,FNewhaven arrested on 31 October on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of encouraging an offence is
OL,21,Falso released on bail until 30 April.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
